	\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is no
	t required.\n\nDetailed Description: Early Learning is a great way for tod
	dlers and their families to develop learning\, literacy\, and language ski
	lls as well as community with other families.\, We play with toys\, share 
	books\, socialize\, and have engaging\, educational activities that help k
	ids and their caregivers grow together.\n\nEvent Logistics: Registration i
	s not required but these programs are very popular and the room capacity c
	an fill up quickly.\, Families of all ages are welcome\, though this early
	 learning program is intended for youth aged 1-3\, their caregivers and fa
	milies.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n\nprograms.\
	n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor ca
