DESCRIPTION:Description The Minority Veterans' monthly Creative Writing Gro
	up is a space to experiment\, imagine\, and build. Writers of all levels a
	re invited to explore fiction\, poetry\, and other creative forms through 
	guided prompts and optional sharing. Whether you're starting fresh or refi
	ning your skills\, this group offers a supportive environment to write\, l
	earn\, and create together.All are welcome\, including veterans\, active-d
	uty\, military family members\, and allies. Snacks and beverages will be a
	vailable. Free parking.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
