SUMMARY:Join Week 2026: Serve the Block
DTSTAMP:20260214T003621Z
DTSTART:20260221T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Serve the Block is a hands-on community service experience cent
	ered on food security and care for our neighbors —because access to basic 
	food and daily necessities should never be out of reach. \n\nVolunteers wi
	ll work along the Culinary Staff at Tabernacle Missionary Baptist Church t
	o create basic hygiene kits and prepare bag lunches for distribution to Se
	attle’s unhoused community. \n\nThis in-person service project is part of 
	Join Week 2026\, a series of events inviting prospective and current membe
	rs to experience the mission\, impact\, and community of the Urban League 
	of Metropolitan Seattle Young Professionals.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
