	he following weekend\, February 21–22\, at the Seattle Aquarium for our Oc
	topus Weekends!  Discover more about these incredible creatures\, learn ab
	out octopus behavior and anatomy\, and enjoy hands-on activities and speci
	al talks. Connect with an octopus face-to-face and find out why we think t
	hese are some of the coolest animals in the ocean.  Learn more and plan yo
	ur visit on our website: https://www.seattleaquarium.org/events/octopus-we
	ekend\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
