	al talks. Connect with an octopus face-to-face and find out why we think t
	hese are some of the coolest animals in the ocean.  Learn more and plan yo
	ur visit on our website: https://www.seattleaquarium.org/events/octopus-we
	ekend\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/octopus-weekend-february-
	21-22/18079834/2026-02-21T00
LOCATION:Seattle Aquarium\, 1483 Alaskan Way\, Pier 59\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H30M
END:VEVENT
