UID:R3MVoPChJXPGITzv6hANN
SUMMARY:Color Bundle: Ecoprint on Fabric
DTSTAMP:20260214T003621Z
DTSTART:20260222T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Taught by Atenas Morales. Get ready for a fun and quick experie
	nce! In this workshop the focus is on the creative experience\, allowing y
	ou to dive into eco-printing in a relaxed and expressive way. Participants
	 will learn to eco-print on a pre-mordanted cellulose bandana\, creating u
	nique pieces full of color and texture. It’s the perfect way to start expl
	oring eco-printing in a short amount of time\, enjoying creativity and tak
	ing home a one-of-a-kind botanical treasure. $59.50 BBGS Members/$85 Non-M
	embers. \n\nAtenas Morales is a textile and botanical artist whose journey
	 spans Mexico\, Spain\, and the Pacific Northwest.  Visit the website.\n\n
	From SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/color-bundle-ecoprint-on-
	fabric/17923219/2026-02-22T00
LOCATION:Bellevue Botanical Garden\, 12001 Main St\, Bellevue\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
