BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Urts9_oOL8V3FioX61bOP
SUMMARY:Baking Fundamentals: Cookies\, Cakes\, Custards and More
DTSTAMP:20260214T003621Z
DTSTART:20260225T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Would you like to be able to make a variety of beautiful and de
	licious baked treats with confidence? Gain fundamental skills and knowledg
	e for baking in this hands-on class.\n\nWe will learn about ingredients\, 
	interactions\, and techniques\, using a variety of mixing methods\, recipe
	s\, and best practices. And we will make a broad range of yummy foods\, su
	ch as muffins\, biscuits\, sponges\, chiffons\, angel food cakes\, quiche\
	, pâte à choux\, custards\, crèmes\, pastry doughs\, pies\, tarts\, layer 
	cakes\, frostings\, meringue\, buttercreams\, and specialty desserts.\n\nE
	njoy making delectable baked goods\, both sweet and savory. We will also d
	iscuss alternative ingredients for people with restrictive diets\, food se
	nsitivities\, and food allergies.\n\nTake advantage of the large\, well-eq
	uipped kitchen at Seattle Central's Culinary Academy. Learn some of the mo
	st useful tips from an experienced chef\, and develop practices for workin
	g in a clean\, safe\, and efficient way.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/baking-fundamentals-cooki
	es-cakes-custards-and-more/17755204/2026-02-24T00
LOCATION:Seattle Central College Continuing Education\, 1701 Broadway\, Sea
	ttle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:JBSGF5F-5BoXqzycqWXCp
SUMMARY:Southside Business Awards Night
DTSTAMP:20260214T003621Z
DTSTART:20260225T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:We're proud to announce the 2025 Southside Business Award Nomin
	ations\, a special evening dedicated to recognizing the outstanding achiev
	ements of businesses\, organizations\, and community leaders across the Se
	attle Southside region. This signature annual event will spotlight excelle
	nce across three key award categories: Seattle Southside Leadership Awards
	 - Presented by the Chamber\, these awards honor exceptional leadership an
	d impact in categories such as Business of the Year\, Small Business of th
	e Year\, New Business of the Year\, Non-Profit of the Year\, Community Imp
	act\, Emerging Leader\, Employer of the Year\, Workforce Development\, Cus
	tomer Service Excellence\, and Ambassador of the Year. Submit nominations 
	here! Hospitality Heroes - Presented by Explore Seattle Southside to celeb
	rate the dedicated individuals and teams who help create memorable and sea
	mless experiences for visitors to our region. Nominate a behind-the-scenes
	 star who goes the extra mile to make our community feel welcoming and hos
	pitable. Nominate Here Best of Seattle Southside - Recognizing culinary ex
	cellence in ten categories\, this award celebrates top food and beverage b
	usinesses located in the cities of Des Moines\, SeaTac\, and Tukwila-areas
	 actively promoted by Explore Seattle Southside. Vote Here Whether you're 
	a nominee\, a business supporter\, or someone passionate about community s
	uccess\, this event offers a night of meaningful recognition\, connection\
	, and celebration. Join us in honoring those who are shaping the future of
	 the Southside.\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/southside-business-awards
	-night/17665296/2026-02-24T00
LOCATION:Marriott\, SeaTac\, 3201 S 176th St\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
