	e and walk away with simple tools to support your body and mind. Yoga mats
	 will be provided\, all you need are clothes comfy enough to stretch in! D
	ay-of\, meet Jennifer inside of Sweatbox Yoga at the bottom of the small s
	tairwell at 10am. RSVP Here\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
